trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: 속성에 대 한 디자인 타임 편집기 시트 나타냅니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 디자인 타임에 디자이너 호스트의 UI에 식입니다.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor> class together with the RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a `RouteUrl` expression, and to combine the selected expression property values into a `RouteUrl` expression.
trans-unit.target: 비주얼 디자이너에서 사용 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>의 개별 속성을 선택 하려면 RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet 클래스와 함께 클래스는 `RouteUrl` 식에는 선택한 식 속성 값을 결합 하 고는 `RouteUrl` 식.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드 RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet 개체를 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a `RouteUrl` expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 식 대화 상자, 컨트롤 속성을 선택 하 고에 바인딩할 경우에 `RouteUrl` 식, 호출 하 여 비주얼 디자이너는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 비주얼 디자이너를 사용 하 여 반환된 된 RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet 개체에 대 한는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the properties are selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to combine the properties into a `RouteUrl` expression string.
trans-unit.target: 비주얼 디자이너를 호출 하는 속성을 선택 하면는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>속성을 결합 하는 메서드는 `RouteUrl` 식 문자열입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property is not specified.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>경우 속성을 지정 해야는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>속성이 지정 되지 않았습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> is not specified.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>경우 속성을 지정 해야는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>지정 되지 않았습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both properties may be specified.
trans-unit.target: 두 속성을 지정할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property values are set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: 초기 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>입력을 사용 하 여 속성 값을 설정 `expression` 문자열.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>속성은 입력을 사용 하 여 `serviceProvider` 구현.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 식, 식 편집기 시트를 초기화 하는 데 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services.
trans-unit.target: 추가 디자인 타임 서비스를 얻기 위해 사용 되는 디자이너 호스트에서 제공 하는 서비스 공급자 구현

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression that is formed by the expression editor sheet property values.
trans-unit.target: 반환 된 <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 식 편집기 시트 속성 값으로 구성 되는 식입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string for the current settings in the sheet.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 시트의 현재 설정에 대 한 식 문자열입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid.
trans-unit.target: 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다 여부는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 식 문자열이 유효한 지 합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>경우는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> 식 문자열은 유효 하지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.target: URL에 대해 생성 되는 경로의 이름을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the route that a URL is to be generated for.
trans-unit.target: URL에 대해 생성 되는 경로의 이름입니다.

trans-unit.target: URL 매개 변수 이름 및 값을 경로에서 URL을 생성 하는 데 사용할 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The URL parameter names and values that are to be used to generate a URL from a route.
trans-unit.target: URL 매개 변수 이름과 경로에서 URL을 생성 하는 데 사용할 값입니다.
